latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We have documented this beautiful wedding of Priyanka and Gaurav. 
.

Jadon Hasdi, Bhulekha menu Painda Ve
Haseya Ch Tu Hasda 
Lamiyan si Vaatan Channa
Nere Nere Aaea Tu 
Akhiyan De Raahi Aa Ke
Dil Ch Samayeya Tu

When i laugh i get delusional..
For i feel you laughing (with me) in my laughter..
Dear.. the path was too long
You came closer and closer..
Through the way of eyes..
you made a way into my heart..

Jadon Puchdi aa Piyar Diyan Gallan Ve
Hauli Hauli tu dasda
Inna Akhiyan Ch Paavan Kive Kajla Ve
Akhiyan Ch Tu Vasda

When i ask you about the lovetalks..
You whisper to me softly.
How do i wear kohl on my eyes..
when it’s you (who resides) in my eyes..

Masa Masa Jindari Main Pyar� vich Rangi Ve
Aj Menu Jaapda Main..
tere Naal mangi Ve
Aj Khushiyan da Ho Gea Savera Ve
Gam Saathon Door Nasda

With much struggle I’ve painted life with love..
Today i have realized..
I’m meant to be with you..
Today it’s the dawn of happiness (contentment)

Inna Akhiyan Ch Paavan Kive Kajla Ve
Akhiyan Ch Tu Vasda...
How do i wear kohl on my eyes..
when it’s you (who resides) in my eyes. 
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Dear Sanabh,
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
“As I walk you down the aisle, I see my dream come to reality. A Dream that every girl father live to fulfill, and this moment I think of a thousand memories that come to my mind.
And the moment you opened your eyes and looked at me, the gentle touch of your little fingers on my face, your playful arms reaching out to carried and comforted and Now, As I give away My Most Precious Daughter My Kanya, I feel my hearts to the deep, I feel lump in my throat, I feel the tears tickle down my face But all the faiths away in comparison to the look of the Gorgeous Bride beside me a beautiful human being that I am so proud off.
Let the tears turn into smiles, pleten your bonds, make equally strong ties of. Let the two family merges ONE with these beautiful Vows a Handover to you Kunal a mist delicate a priceless possession my Darling Daughter. 
The light of my eyes, the strength of my arms, and last but not the least MY Life. 
God Bless You Both.. As you empower on this beautiful journey of togetherness.

latestPosts.caption:
SAMIHAH & ZAID 

 “In the soft greens of Detroit, he didn’t just walk behind her— he followed her story.
With every step,
Samihah’s silence said more than words ever could.
And Zaid…
Zaid listened—with his hands, his heart,
and the way he held on to more than just fabric.
This wasn’t a wedding—it was a quiet unfolding.
Of love, Of grace, Of forever.”
